#: _posts/2023-01-31-quarkus-3-7-released.adoc
msgid "Quarkus 3.7 - Java 17 baseline, Hibernate ORM 6.4, @MeterTag..."
msgstr ""

#: _posts/2023-01-31-quarkus-3-7-released.adoc
msgid "We released Quarkus 3.7 which requires Java 17+, updates to Hibernate ORM 6.4, supports Micrometer @MeterTag and much more. 3.6.9 was also released to address two CVEs."
msgstr ""

#: _posts/2023-01-31-quarkus-3-7-released.adoc
msgid "It is with great pleasure that we are announcing the release of Quarkus 3.7."
msgstr ""

#: _posts/2023-01-31-quarkus-3-7-released.adoc
msgid ""
"With Quarkus 3.7, we begin the journey that will lead to Quarkus 3.8 being the next LTS version of Quarkus.\n"
"We strongly encourage you to update to this version and provide feedback to make our next LTS version strong and stable."
msgstr ""

